so that explains it.

767
00:35:43,119 --> 00:35:44,355
You guys walked in together.

768
00:35:44,388 --> 00:35:45,955
-I'm gonna just call her.
-Uh, maybe don't.

769
00:35:45,988 --> 00:35:47,291
-(knocking at door)
-Don't do that.

770
00:35:47,324 --> 00:35:48,359
'Cause, you know,
we're just... we're chatting.

771
00:35:48,392 --> 00:35:49,293
