-(phone beeps)

774
00:35:57,200 --> 00:35:59,536
-NIKKI: Hey, Bear.
-Oh.

775
00:35:59,570 --> 00:36:01,070
-(chuckles): Hey.
-I had to shower,

776
00:36:01,104 --> 00:36:03,106
and I didn't know what to wear.

777
00:36:03,940 --> 00:36:05,542
