you were freaked out.

780
00:36:10,514 --> 00:36:14,251
I'm just glad I could
be there, I guess.

781
00:36:14,284 --> 00:36:18,988
Yeah, um, so I probably
shouldn't have taken anything.

782
00:36:22,459 --> 00:36:24,328
So...

783
00:36:24,361 --> 00:36:27,096
I was on MDMA.

784
00:36:27,765 --> 00:36:30,967
-Right.
-And... wasted.

785
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:32,935
(chuckles):
That's okay.

786
00:36:34,003 --> 00:36:35,972
Do you...

787
00:36:36,005 --> 00:36:38,675
remember...

788
00:36:38,709 --> 00:36:40,377
stuff?

789
00:36:41,211 --> 00:36:43,480
Some of it. I mean...

790
00:36:43,514 --> 00:36:46,683
So, if I was weird, that's why,
and my dad made me a mess,

791
00:36:46,717 --> 00:36:49,051
