wouldn't have done otherwise.

792
00:36:49,085 --> 00:36:50,987
And I'm not saying
that you took advantage of me.

793
00:36:51,020 --> 00:36:53,524
Nikki, I didn't know
you were on drugs.

794
00:36:53,557 --> 00:36:55,225
That's what I'm saying.
I'm not saying that.

795
00:36:55,259 --> 00:36:57,461
