-You took advantage of me.

796
00:36:57,494 --> 00:36:59,430
I don't think... I didn't.

797
00:36:59,463 --> 00:37:00,431
I know. That's why...

798
00:37:00,464 --> 00:37:02,533
-I'm saying you didn't.
-Okay.

799
00:37:02,566 --> 00:37:04,133
Good.

800
00:37:04,167 --> 00:37:08,439
I just, um, don't like to...

801
00:37:09,606 --> 00:37:11,107
I really like what we have,

802
00:37:11,140 --> 00:37:12,743
and I want to be honest
about some things,

803
00:37:12,776 --> 00:37:15,044
and it's really important
for me.

804
00:37:15,077 --> 00:37:18,147
It's okay.
Um, you know, I-I get it.

805
00:37:19,316 --> 00:37:20,983
I get it.

806
00:37:22,219 --> 00:37:24,455
