807
00:37:24,488 --> 00:37:26,523
♪ ♪

808
00:37:29,058 --> 00:37:30,993
(stammers)

809
00:37:32,061 --> 00:37:33,963
No, I...

810
00:37:34,765 --> 00:37:36,966
