Would it freak you out
if I said yes?

812
00:37:44,608 --> 00:37:46,577
(chuckles softly)

813
00:37:50,247 --> 00:37:52,649
How long have you felt that way?

814
00:37:52,683 --> 00:37:54,551
It's just happened over time.

815
00:37:54,585 --> 00:37:57,186
Started during Christmas, and...

816
00:37:57,221 --> 00:37:58,755
I don't know, it just...

817
00:37:58,789 --> 00:38:01,391
Then, last night,
I saw what we could...

818
00:38:07,397 --> 00:38:09,366
Do you have feelings for me?

819
00:38:18,442 --> 00:38:20,142
Yeah, I do.

820
00:38:20,176 --> 00:38:22,412
♪ ♪

821
00:38:23,580 --> 00:38:26,015
(voices muted)

822
00:38:32,623 --> 00:38:35,225
♪ ♪

823
00:38:40,096 --> 00:38:44,033
♪ ♪

824
00:38:53,510 --> 00:38:55,546
♪ ♪

825
00:39:11,328 --> 00:39:14,096
And I wrote, "In a band,"
and then she made me change it.

826
00:39:14,130 --> 00:39:15,499
-Yeah.
-Bitch. (laughs)

827
00:39:15,532 --> 00:39:17,467
And then you leaned in,
and you whispered...

828
00:39:17,501 --> 00:39:19,636
BOTH:
"I'll be in your band."

829
00:39:19,670 --> 00:39:21,371
(both laugh)

830
00:39:21,405 --> 00:39:23,340
Yeah.

831
00:39:24,808 --> 00:39:26,476
How's your dad doing?

832
00:39:27,911 --> 00:39:30,547
-Can we not talk about that?
-(cell phone vibrating)

833
00:39:30,581 --> 00:39:32,081
Okay.

834
00:39:33,717 --> 00:39:35,452
Um...

835
00:39:35,485 --> 00:39:38,822
so what do you want to do?

836
00:39:38,855 --> 00:39:41,123
I mean, I never really asked.

837
00:39:41,157 --> 00:39:43,260
Well, that's not all your fault.

838
00:39:43,293 --> 00:39:46,195
I mean, I'm kind of private,
I guess.

839
00:39:46,229 --> 00:39:47,764
You guess?

840
