he's called.

870
00:40:51,328 --> 00:40:52,596
I'll be right back.

871
00:40:53,397 --> 00:40:56,566
-What is it, dude? I'm busy.
-IAN: Oh, busy doing Nikki?

872
00:40:56,600 --> 00:40:57,834
What do you want?

873
00:40:57,868 --> 00:41:00,537
Okay, so, um...

874
00:41:00,570 --> 00:41:02,305
-What is it?
-(Ian stammers)

875
