953
00:46:40,877 --> 00:46:43,580
-Can you come back to bed?
-No, no.

954
00:46:49,119 --> 00:46:50,787
-Nikki.
-No.

955
00:46:54,824 --> 00:46:57,794
(crying):
I don't like my dreams.

956
00:46:59,029 --> 00:47:01,798
(sobbing)

957
00:47:07,170 --> 00:47:11,808
I feel like you don't love me
as much as I do.

958
00:47:11,841 --> 00:47:16,679
Like it's not mutual.

959
00:47:17,348 --> 00:47:19,916
No, I... I do.

960
00:47:19,949 --> 00:47:22,886
-Just come back to bed.
-(sobbing continues)

961
00:47:22,919 --> 00:47:24,687
Please?

962
00:47:25,655 --> 00:47:27,690
(sobbing stops)

963
00:47:32,396 --> 00:47:35,131
(crying):
Go back to sleep.

964
00:47:35,165 --> 00:47:36,733
(Nikki sobs softly)

965
00:47:59,989 --> 00:48:03,827
-Why don't you love me?!
-(gasps)

966
00:48:03,860 --> 00:48:06,763
Nikki? Nikki, where are you?

967
00:48:08,965 --> 00:48:11,768
(rapid, trembling breaths)

968
00:48:15,239 --> 00:48:16,806
