969
00:48:21,744 --> 00:48:23,880
Nikki, what are you doing?

970
00:48:28,118 --> 00:48:29,752
Nikki.

971
00:48:31,888 --> 00:48:33,990
No, what-what do you
want me to do?

972
00:48:35,226 --> 00:48:36,993
For Sandy, okay?

973
00:48:43,334 --> 00:48:45,735
♪ ♪

974
00:49:04,388 --> 00:49:07,056
Stay!

975
00:49:11,295 --> 00:49:13,663
(insects trilling)

976
00:49:15,399 --> 00:49:17,800
(birds chirping)

977
00:49:26,809 --> 00:49:28,745
What the fuck?

978
00:49:41,492 --> 00:49:43,793
-Morning.
-NIKKI: Morning.

979
00:49:46,129 --> 00:49:47,697
(clears throat)

980
00:49:49,366 --> 00:49:51,134
Um...

981
00:49:51,167 --> 00:49:52,702
Yeah?

982
00:49:55,772 --> 00:49:58,275
Did you cut my hair?

983
00:49:58,309 --> 00:49:59,842
Yeah.

984
00:50:03,980 --> 00:50:06,816
Let's not do that.

985
00:50:12,256 --> 00:50:13,923
Okay.

986
00:50:18,928 --> 00:50:20,997
