987
00:50:21,030 --> 00:50:22,131
Oh.

988
00:50:22,165 --> 00:50:23,066
(Nikki laughs)

989
00:50:23,099 --> 00:50:26,836
Oh, oh, can-can we talk
about last night?

990
00:50:26,869 --> 00:50:29,206
(sighs) I know.

991
00:50:29,240 --> 00:50:30,374
I know. I know.

992
00:50:30,407 --> 00:50:31,808
It was kind of weird.

993
00:50:31,841 --> 00:50:32,976
Right? (chuckles)

994
00:50:33,009 --> 00:50:35,246
Yeah. I'm so sorry.

995
00:50:36,179 --> 00:50:38,848
Okay, good,
'cause if I'm being honest,

996
00:50:38,881 --> 00:50:40,351
it was kind of terrifying.

997
00:50:40,384 --> 00:50:41,851
Oh, my God.

998
00:50:42,453 --> 00:50:44,988
I'm so sorry.

999
00:50:45,021 --> 00:50:48,225
I had a bad dream, and I just...

1000
00:50:53,597 --> 00:50:56,065
-You what?
-How's this?

1001
00:51:06,377 --> 00:51:07,944
Not great.

1002
00:51:09,145 --> 00:51:10,079
Okay.

1003
00:51:10,113 --> 00:51:11,482
-Listen, Nikki.
-Come here.

1004
00:51:11,515 --> 00:51:13,816
-I think...
-Come here.

1005
00:51:13,850 --> 00:51:15,219
Listen.

1006
00:51:26,530 --> 00:51:28,831
(Bear's breath trembling)

1007
00:51:28,865 --> 00:51:30,567
I love you.

1008
00:51:30,601 --> 00:51:32,403
I love you, too.

1009
00:51:33,002 --> 00:51:35,439
-So, so, so, so...
-Okay, okay, okay, okay.

1010
00:51:35,472 --> 00:51:38,174
Good. Good.

1011
00:51:38,208 --> 00:51:40,444
So, will you promise me
something?

1012
00:51:40,477 --> 00:51:41,911
Yes.

1013
00:51:41,944 --> 00:51:44,281
No more weird stuff.

1014
00:51:44,315 --> 00:51:45,882
All right?

1015
00:51:45,915 --> 00:51:47,484
No more watching me
while I sleep

1016
